(12, 'Pohon Zaitun Dalam Ruangan', 'The Olive Tree (Olea Europaea \'Mission\') is an excellent ornamental indoor tree with a gray-barked trunk that becomes gnarled and knobby with silvery-leafed branches. This tree boasts the smallest pits and is a cold-resistant variety. Harvesting for table olives will start in late October through November. Oil production occurs from mid-December through February, and the olives are harvested. ...', 'pohon-zaitun-dalam-ruangan', 9, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/files/Pl_6in_Olive_Detail_01_large.jpg?v=1727846458', 739500, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
