(15, 'Lily Perdamaian', 'This beautiful Peace Lily plant (Spathiphyllum) will bring elegance and content to any home. As well as being a certified peace symbol — thanks to their striking white flowers — they are also renowned for their air-purifying abilities. People often gift this plant as a sign of everlasting life to people facing loss or hardship. Easy to care for, this indoor plant prefers partial shade and just ...', 'lily-perdamaian', 53, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/products/PeaceLily_Detail2_10_large.jpg?v=1678465377', 483750, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
(16, 'Pothos Emas Favorit Semua Orang', 'The Golden Pothos is one of the worlds\' best-selling plants, and for a good reason! They are basically impossible to kill and thrives in situations other plants can\'t handle. Golden pothos is so low-maintenance they have a reputation for being impossible to kill — hence their nickname, devil\'s ivy. They don\'t need much water, and they are quite happy in darker parts of your home. They can ...', 'pothos-emas-favorit-semua-orang', 96, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/products/pl_GoldenPothos_8IN_po_grower_detail-1_large.jpg?v=1636583146', 483750, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
(17, 'Chinese Money Tree Plant (Pilea Peperomioides)', 'We can\'t promise that the Chinese money plant (Pilea Peperomioides) will bring you good fortune, but we can say they\'ll add instant style to any room. As well as being one of the most popular plants for Feng Shui, they are also famous with fans of Scandi design — They are Norway\'s favorite sill plant. Chinese money plants are also easy to care for and fun to grow. What\'s not to love?', 'chinese-money-tree-plant', 71, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/products/MoneyPlant_6_DTL1_57977528-7ede-4883-8ab0-76a96cdc93f7_large.jpg?v=1672248604', 645000, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
(18, 'Variegated Sansevieria Laurentii (Snake Plant)', 'We know there are different types of Snake Plants, and it can be tough to know which one to pick. The variegated Snake Plants, or Sansevieria Laurentii, stands out for its remarkable durability and ease of care. Known for thriving in various conditions, these plants are visually appealing and robust – perfect for \'set and forget\' care. They are ideal for enhancing your personal green oasis and ...', 'variegated-sansevieria-laurentii', 73, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/products/pl_VariegatedLaurentii_6IN_po_grower_detail-2_large.jpg?v=1636588013', 645000, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
(19, 'Rosemary Christmas Tree', 'Enjoy the intense aromatic smell of Rosmarinus officinalis (Rosemary) as you brush them with your hand or along the garden path. Their gray-green, needle-like leaves grow up to 1.5\" long and are closely spaced together. White or blue flowers eventually bloom on this herb, making them more appealing in the garden. Use as an ornamental in the garden or a garden pot. Add them to your culinary ...', 'rosemary-christmas-tree', 46, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/products/Pl_6in_Rosemary_Detail_02_large.jpg?v=1669412249', 609000, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
(20, 'Red Christmas Cactus', 'Enjoy this tropical bloomer, Schlumbergera bridgesii or Christmas cactus in the dead of winter with their beautiful, exotic colored blooms profusely having a party on top of the succulent leaves! No needles to prick the fingers, just flattened stems with profuse blooms growing just in time for the holidays! Bring some \'happy\' and \'merry\' in with this popular indoor plant!', 'red-christmas-cactus', 79, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/products/pl_ChristmasCactus_4IN_po_grower_detail-1_large.jpg?v=1636485888', 548250, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
(21, 'Giant Bird of Paradise', 'Commonly known as the Giant White Bird of Paradise, the Strelitzia Nicolai is a flowering plant that is native to South Africa. They are similar to the Orange Bird of Paradise but can grow to be much, much taller.', 'giant-bird-of-paradise', 18, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/products/pl_giantbirdofparadise_5gal_po_grower_detail-1_large.jpg?v=1659470452', 645000, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
(22, 'Guzmania Bromeliad', 'Guzmania Bromeliads add significant intrigue, color and beauty to your Green Space. They have long, slender evergreen leaves that are topped by a single brilliant inflorescence of tongue-like petals. The bloom will be deep red, maroon, orange, pink, or yellow, or some combination thereof. Bromeliad flowers can last 3 to 6 months, but they typically flower just once. Fun Fact: The Guzmania ...', 'guzmania-bromeliad', 9, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/products/pl_bromeliad_6IN_po_grower_detail-1_b7c0a76b-0678-4609-9b7d-121fd31eec61_large.jpg?v=1658349219', 483750, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
(23, 'Fiddle Leaf Fig Tree (Ficus Lyrata)', 'Fiddle Leaf Figs, \'Ficus Lyrata\', are gorgeous plants known for their large leaves and vibrant green colors.   With their big broad leaves, the fiddle leaf fig is definitely one of the most iconic house plants out there. They are also one of the most popular and has become one of the biggest home decor trends in all houseplant history.  They are a little \"high maintenance\" - preferring a more ...', 'fiddle-leaf-fig-tree', 58, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/files/Pl_10in_Ficus-Lyrata_Detail_02_large.jpg?v=1689030423', 870000, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
(24, 'Calathea Rattlesnake', 'The Rattlesnake Plant (Calathea lancifolia) is one you\'ll kick up your boots over! His distinctive markings of limelight green with darker brush strokes seemingly painted onto the leaf will get you to back up and dismount from your horse! Once evening comes and dusk is near, the leaves stand straight up to reveal the hidden burgundy leaf underside. It\'s like having two plants in one! No ...', 'calathea-rattlesnake', 57, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/files/Pl_6in_Calathea-Lancifolia_Detail_01_large.jpg?v=1718393906', 645000, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
(25, 'Cast Iron Plant', 'The Cast Iron Plant, scientifically known as Aspidistra elatior, is incredibly low-maintenance and can tolerate a range of conditions, including low light, irregular watering, and varying humidity levels. This makes it perfect for even the most forgetful plant parents!', 'cast-iron-plant', 67, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/files/6in_Cast-Iron-Plant_Detail_02_large.jpg?v=1724103935', 870000, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
(26, 'Boston Fern Plant', 'Bushy and beautiful, the Boston fern will add some woodland charm to your home. A natural air purifier, they are super efficient at removing chemicals like formaldehyde from the air. They love indirect light and lots of humidity — making them a natural choice for your bathroom. Please place them in a hanging basket and let their delicate fronds drape over the sides.', 'boston-fern-plant', 15, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/products/pl_BostonFern_6IN_po_grower1_detail-2_large.jpg?v=1658863483', 870000, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
(27, 'Watermelon Peperomia', 'The watermelon peperomia is the absolute best name for this plant because each leaf looks like a tiny watermelon. They have waxy, green, and silver-striped leaves attached to short, reddish-purple stems. This peperomia variety is the perfect addition to your indoor plant collection. The watermelon peperomia is easy to grow and is very adaptable, making them great for beginners. They fill up ...', 'watermelon-peperomia', 92, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/products/pl_pepperonia_watermelon_6IN_po_grower_detail-1_large.jpg?v=1628274343', 645000, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
(28, 'Areca Palm Indoor Tree', 'Enjoy the soft, fine textured arching fronds of the Areca palm (Dypsis lutescens) as an indoor house plant or in the garden in warmer zones of the country. Place them where there is headroom to grow, like in a foyer stairwell or outside porch area in a container.', 'areca-palm-indoor-tree', 24, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/products/pl_AreciaButterflyPalm_4IN_po_grower-detail-1_large.jpg?v=1658349115', 645000, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
(29, 'Pink Aechmea Bromeliad', 'The Pink Aechmea Bromeliad is a special Bromeliad because they are uniquely tropical and rare looking. This bromeliad’s name is derived from a Greek word for “spear,” and the name is quite fitting. This Aechmea fasciata, with a flower head that is predominately pink, is one of the most popular bromeliads on the market.   Bromeliad flowers can last 3 to 6 months, but they typically flower just ...', 'pink-aechmea-bromeliad', 88, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/products/BromeliadAechmeaPink_6IN_po_grower_detail-1_large.jpg?v=1639596578', 652500, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
(30, 'Monstera Deliciosa (Split Leaf Philodendron)', 'It doesn\'t get more iconic than the swiss cheese plant. Also known as Monstera Deliciosa, they are famous in interior design circles for their notched leaves. This large one will instantly bring on-trend jungle vibes to your home. They love to spread out, so give them plenty of space and use a coir pole to keep them upright. They are easy to care for and make an ideal first houseplant.', 'monstera-deliciosa', 33, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/products/pl_SplitLeafPhilodendron_6IN_po_grower_detail-2_large.jpg?v=1630442638', 645000, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
