(32, 'Norfolk Island Pine', 'Our Norfolk Pine (Araucaria heterophylla) is a party waiting to happen! He\'s ready for all manner of decoration and costume. His upright trunk sits erect with his pyramidal shape. His evergreen form holds whorled, parallel branches (typically 5 branches per whorl) in layers. He will do double-duty for the sights of the season as well as a great houseplant throughout the year growing up to 3-5\' ...', 'norfolk-island-pine', 91, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/products/pl_UnknownTree_10IN_po_grower_detail-1_large.jpg?v=1637085710', 483750, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
(33, 'Peacock Plant (Calathea)', 'When it comes to showmanship, you can\'t go wrong with peacock plants. Watermelon colors of dark red on the bottom and variegated green and yellow on the top make their foliage stand out. Officially called Calathea Medallion Roseopicta, these Brazilian beauties have earned the nickname \'prayer plants\'. This is because they raise and lower their leaves throughout the day as if they\'re ...', 'peacock-plant', 86, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/products/1080PeacockCloseUp_large.jpg?v=1679674875', 645000, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
(34, 'Ruby Rubber Tree Plant', 'Enhance your space with the Ruby Rubber Tree (Ficus elastica \'Ruby\'), a versatile indoor tree perfect for both beginners and experienced plant lovers. Known for its ease of care, this rubber tree plant variety can impressively grow up to 8 feet indoors, making it a prime choice for those seeking a large, full-grown indoor tree. The Ruby Rubber Tree is not just an attractive indoor tree; it ...', 'ruby-rubber-tree-plant', 93, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/products/pl_ficuselasticaruby_6IN_po_basket_detail-2_large.jpg?v=1630437128', 870000, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
(35, 'Ponytail Palm Tree', 'Our ponytail palm plants for delivery will add a quirky touch to any room. They have thin, curly leaves that gently tumble down past their thick stalk. Although they looks utterly whimsical, they are actually low maintenance and one of our favorite starter plants. They enjoy direct sunlight and can live on your patio if you live in USDA hardiness zones 9 through 11.', 'ponytail-palm-tree', 75, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/products/pl_PonytailPalm_5Gal_pl_grower_detail-1_large.jpg?v=1658349251', 870000, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
(36, 'Monstera Thai Constellation', 'The rare and coveted Monstera Thai Constellation has finally arrived! A unique relative of the classic Monstera Deliciosa, each leaf is a piece of art, splashed with creamy white and lush green, resembling a night sky filled with twinkling stars. Highly sought after by collectors, the Monstera Thai Constellation has limited inventory, so get your hands on it while you can!', 'monstera-thai-constellation', 27, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/files/Pl_6in_Monstera-Thai-Constellation_Detail_02_large.jpg?v=1718334802', 1725000, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
(37, 'Lipstick Plant', 'Lipstick Plant (Aeschynanthus radicans) bestows that beauty accessory everyone loves, even a James Dean wannabe! We love how she reminds us to put our best lips forward and pucker up for a smack. She produces what looks like miniature red lipstick tubes on her green vines. She blooms throughout the spring and summer, so fertilize monthly for that classic color to flourish. She can have vines ...', 'lipstick-plant', 71, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/products/pl_LipstickPlant_6IN_po_grower_detail-1_large.jpg?v=1642792145', 870000, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
(38, 'Pink Christmas Cactus', 'Enjoy this tropical bloomer, Schlumbergera bridgesii or Christmas cactus in the dead of winter with their beautiful, exotic colored blooms profusely having a party on top of the succulent leaves! No needles to prick the fingers, just flattened stems with profuse blooms growing just in time for the holidays! Bring some \'happy\' and \'merry\' in with this popular indoor plant!', 'pink-christmas-cactus', 66, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/files/Pl_4in_Christmas-Cactus-Pink_Detail_01_large.jpg?v=1700554002', 451500, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
(39, 'Leyland Cypress Christmas Tree', 'This attractive miniature Christmas tree has flattened sprays of gray-green foliage on slender upright branches. The Leyland Cypress is known to be a fast grower, achieving 24 - 48 inches of growth in just one year when given the right conditions! Theoretically, this miniature Christmas tree could be a full-sized living Christmas tree next year! We dare you to try!', 'leyland-cypress-christmas-tree', 31, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/files/Pl_6in_Leyland-Cypress_Detail_01_large.jpg?v=1699372894', 451500, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
(40, 'ZZ Plant', 'The ZZ plant is an excellent low-maintenance indoor plant, so low-maintenance that we like to say they almost thrive on neglect! You can place them almost anywhere, and they will grow, but they do appreciate a little bit of light now and then. Wherever they go, they are a tasteful and classy addition to your Green Space. Our ZZ plant is the ideal choice for inexperienced plant parents, too. ...', 'zz-plant', 27, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/products/pl_zz_plant_6IN_po_grower_detail_2_large.jpg?v=1697001498', 645000, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
(41, 'Swiss Cheese Monstera Plant', 'The Swiss Cheese Plant (Monstera Adansonii) is one of those plants everyone wants to have because of its unusual leaves. Their leaves have swiss-cheese-like holes that developed due to their native tropical rainforest environment to help withstand heavy rainfall and wind passing through them. Their aerial roots help them climb upwards or be a hanging vine, gathering nutrition and moisture from ...', 'swiss-cheese-monstera-plant', 66, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/products/pl_SwissCheeseMonstera_6IN_po_grower_detail-3_large.jpg?v=1663619035', 645000, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
(42, 'Orange Bird of Paradise', 'Commonly known as the Bird of Paradise, or Crane Flower, the Strelitzia reginae is a flowering plant that is native to the eastern coastlines of South Africa, where they grow wild in patches that can span for miles. An evergreen perennial, they are widely cultivated for their dramatic flowers.', 'orange-bird-of-paradise', 89, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/products/pl_unknown2_6IN_po_grower-detail-2_af506c34-3554-4422-bf69-a0a3c8d6c39b_large.jpg?v=1634576711', 870000, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
(43, 'Pygmy Date Palm Tree', 'This Pygmy Date Palm brings tropical vibes into any space. Also known as the Phoenix Roebelenii pygmy date palm, their name suggests they are small, but this little cutie can grow. Expect heights of six to twelve feet if you look after them well. They originally come from Southeast Asia, so if you live in a USDA Zone 10-11 they\'ll thrive on your patio. Otherwise, they make an excellent indoor ...', 'pygmy-date-palm-tree', 81, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/products/DatePalm_Detail1_10_large.jpg?v=1625772553', 2040000, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
(44, 'Ficus Elastica - Burgundy Rubber Tree', 'The Burgundy Rubber Tree is easy for beginners and a great starter plant! They can quickly grow up to 8\' inside and do best in bright to moderate indirect light. In general these plants leave our nursery when they are 16\" to 28\" tall (depending on the size). They are living plants and actual size may vary depending on the current crop.', 'ficus-elastica--burgundy-rubber-tree', 89, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/products/pl_ficus_burgundy_4IN_po_grower_detail-1_large.jpg?v=1689014784', 645000, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
(45, 'Sansevieria Zeylanica Snake Plant', 'The leading commercial variety of Sansevieria is known and grown for the hemp-like fiber in the leaves. They are an interesting and attractive plant that is also durable for a wide range of conditions. The Zeylanica Snake plant is easy to care for and makes a great addition to your green space. Species of the Sansevieria genus are recommended for air purification – particularly within the home ...', 'sansevieria-zeylanica-snake-plant', 31, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/products/SanSeveriaXeylanica_6_4DTL2_f3ad571a-b024-46a4-84ab-82c3a94c09c8_large.jpg?v=1611783705', 645000, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
(46, 'Spider Plant (Variegated Reverse)', 'Our spider plants bring the lush jungles of Southern Africa to your home. One of the best air purifying plants, we love them for their spiky variegated foliage. They are easy to care for and look great set on a table-top or hung from a macrame sling. You can even keep them out on the patio during summer — just remember to bring them inside if there\'s any risk of frost. Our spiky and ...', 'spider-plant-(variegated-reverse)', 58, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/products/pl_spider_plant_6IN_po_grower_detail-3_large.jpg?v=1697001750', 645000, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
(47, 'Lady Palm', 'A popular houseplant for more than three hundred years, the lady palm (Rhapis Excelsa) instantly brings elegance into any room. They are one of our indoor and outdoor plants — they can grow happily on your patio if you live in USDA hardiness zones 8b through 12. They grow from multiple stems and have fan-shaped fronds, which give them a truly unique look. Not only are they beautiful, but they ...', 'lady-palm', 13, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/products/LadyPalm_10IN_PetFriendly_large.jpg?v=1659470465', 2040000, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
