(51, 'Hindu Hoya Rope Plant', 'The Hindu Rope Plant (Hoya carnosa \'Compacta\") looks like she just came from the salon and had a complete body treatment. Her curly leaves look like a fresh braid of hair unfurling. When she blooms, they look like bows in her hair! Plus, she gives off that irresistible fragrance, her signature cologne. Her waxy leaves are succulent-like, but she still likes her soil to be moist to keep her ...', 'hindu-hoya-rope-plant', 98, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/files/Pl_6in_Hoya-Compacta_Detail_05_large.jpg?v=1719617447', 870000, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
