(53, 'Maranta Red Prayer Plant', 'The Maranta Red Prayer Plant (Maranta Leuconeura) has their own internal clock exemplified in their daily rhythm. They lift their leaves in the evening and lower them in the morning, mimicking praying hands. The broad, oval leaves have two-color variegated spots with red veining on the top side and a reddish color on the bottom side, making them very festive to enjoy in any home or office.', 'maranta-red-prayer-plant', 89, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/products/MarantaRed_Basket_6_large.jpg?v=1616011318', 870000, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
