(56, 'Frosty Fern', 'Delightfully lush and unique, the Frosty Fern (Selaginella kraussiana) brings a wintry charm to your home with its soft, silvery-green foliage that resembles delicate frost-tipped ferns. Known for its love of humidity, this plant thrives in bright, indirect light and makes an excellent addition to bathrooms or terrariums where it can enjoy consistent moisture. Compact and bushy, the Frosty ...', 'frosty-fern', 1, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/files/4in_Frosty-Fern_Detail_03_large.jpg?v=1732518098', 483750, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
(57, 'Lemon Button Fern', 'Add this little \'Lemon Button\' fern to your collection, a smaller version of the Boston fern. Only growing a foot high, they make a beautiful ensemble with other tropicals. They are small, and finely-textured leaves are a nice contrast to larger leaf tropicals.', 'lemon-button-fern', 18, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/products/pl_pellaearotundifoliabuttonfern_4IN_po_grower_detail-1_large.jpg?v=1636585536', 645000, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
