(93, 'Hoya Carnosa Tricolor', 'This beauty sports variegated leaves in shades of green, cream, and pink, creating a captivating display climbing up a trellis. If you\'re lucky, clusters of fragrant, star-shaped flowers sprout out and steal the show!  The Hoya Carnosa Tricolor is a low-maintenance, eye-catching plant, perfect for beginners and green experts alike!', 'hoya-carnosa-tricolor', 86, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/files/Pl_6in_Hoya-Tricolor_Detail_02_large.jpg?v=1719622388', 870000, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
(94, 'Very Buzzy Succulent Garden', 'These buzzy gardens of petite succulents are perfect for sprucing up your tablescapes or sunny windowsill. It\'s always a party with three assorted easy-care succulents planted together in a ceramic pot. Perfectly giftable, perfectly keepable.  The garden container measures 5\" wide by 4\" tall.  *Succulent varieties and color are assorted and may differ slightly from photos', 'very-buzzy-succulent-garden', 44, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/files/Pl_Very-Buzzy-Garden_Baby-Blue-Pot_01_2_large.jpg?v=1727324976', 930000, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
(95, 'Aloe Vera Plant', 'The aloe vera plant (Barbados Aloe) is notorious for being one of the most sought-after succulents worldwide. Its medicinal properties have made it a popular ingredient for various beauty and health products. The Aloe\'s succulent leaves contain rich antioxidant and antibacterial properties in their extract. Bonus—it is a very low-maintenance plant to have in your collection!', 'aloe-vera-plant', 72, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/products/Aloe_DTL_large.jpg?v=1612224061', 870000, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
(96, 'Japanese Birds Nest Fern', 'Japanese Bird\'s Nest Fern (Asplenium antiquum) is among 350 species of ferns in the genus Asplenium. This one differs from Asplenium nidus since the wavy fronds are more uniform in width. The arched frond will reach three feet long in the native environment. Please keep him in humidity and consistently moist soil in bright, indirect light or on a sheltered porch. His interesting wave will ...', 'japanese-birds-nest-fern', 87, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/products/pl_FernAspleniumAntiquum-JapaneseBird_sNest_6IN_po_grower-detail-2_large.jpg?v=1662483984', 870000, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
(97, '2.5 Living Rosemary Spiral Christmas Tree', 'Enjoy the aromatic smell of Rosmarinus officinalis (Rosemary) this holiday season. This unique Christmas Tree will stand out from the rest with its fine-manicured spiral. Perfect as a holiday decoration or as a unique gift!', '2.5-living-rosemary-spiral-christmas-tree', 93, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/files/Pl_10in_Rosemary-Spiral_Detail_06_large.jpg?v=1699241323', 1552500, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
(98, 'Mini Leyland Cypress 4-Pack', 'These adorable trees make for the ultimate stocking stuffers or holiday table decor this year! Leyland Cypress sport flattened sprays of gray-green foliage on slender upright branches. Known to be a fast grower, it can achieve 24 - 48 inches of growth in just one year when given the right conditions! Theoretically, this miniature Christmas tree could be a full-sized living Christmas tree next ...', 'mini-leyland-cypress-4-pack', 47, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/files/Pl_4in_Leyland-4-Pack_Grower_01_large.jpg?v=1701333879', 1875000, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
(99, 'Red Lip Moth Orchid', 'Behold the beauty of the Red Lip Moth Orchid, a masterpiece crafted by nature itself just for us to gaze our eyes on. This exotic orchid boasts not one, but TWO stunning flower spikes ensuring it always steals the show. The best part is, these blooms can last up to 3 months!  We ship our orchids in partial bloom, which means you\'ll see some flowers that haven\'t entirely opened up yet. The ...', 'red-lip-moth-orchid', 23, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/files/P_5in_Red-Lip-Orchid_Detail_02_1_large.jpg?v=1727400905', 816000, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
(100, 'Sansevieria Moonshine', 'Sansevieria Moonshine is a shorter variety of Sansevieria or Snake Plants. They are extremely adaptable, low maintenance, and make for a perfect gift. They are also a great air-purifying plant for plant lovers of all levels!', 'sansevieria-moonshine', 78, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/products/ZZ_4_439_205ed51e-28ca-49af-b8ef-19db8691ed00_large.jpg?v=1611784045', 645000, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
(101, 'Variegated Hoya Heart', 'The Variegated Hoya Heart (Hoya Kerrii) gets their common name from the shape of a single green leaf. Normally vining, this single heart-shaped leaf was rooted without nodes to maintain their single statuesque form. The thick semi-succulent leaves prefer bright indirect light.  This plant is actually a living, rooted leaf. If they do happen to grow, you are one of the lucky ones!', 'variegated-hoya-heart', 41, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/products/pl_variagatedhoyaheart_4IN_po_grower-detail-2_large.jpg?v=1634574414', 645000, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
(102, 'Fresh Cedar Garland', 'May your holiday look wonderful with this gorgeous 12\' cedar garland. Hang it on your mantle, place it on your dining room table, or place it around your windows. The options for this ornamental greenery is limitless! This hand-made, live garland is hand-made and packed fresh with cedar. It will bring the holiday spirit to your home for up to 8 weeks with occasional spritzing.  Fresh-cut ...', 'fresh-cedar-garland', 19, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/products/7-8in_Swag_Holiday_04_large.jpg?v=1699470834', 990000, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
(103, 'Yellow Phalaenopsis Orchid ‘Miraflore’', 'Say hello to the biggest flirt in the Orchid family; the Miraflore Moth Orchid gets your attention with its bright yellow petals and blows you a kiss with its violet-red lips! This gorgeous orchid boasts not one, but TWO stunning flower spikes ensuring it always steals the show. The best part is, these blooms can last up to 3 months! We ship our orchids in partial bloom, which means you\'ll see ...', 'yellow-phalaenopsis-orchid-‘miraflore’', 77, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/files/Pl_5in_Phalaenopsis-Miraflore-Orchid_Detail_04_large.jpg?v=1713237538', 960000, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
(104, 'Petra Croton', 'Add some color to your home with this medium croton petra. This gorgeous tropical plant thrives in brightly lit spots. The more sun they get, the more rainbow shades will appear in their variegated foliage. You can usually expect warm stripes of red, pink, and yellow contrasting with dark green. Bright and bold, they are surprisingly easy to care for. This croton petra is packed with vibrant ...', 'petra-croton', 23, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/products/pl_CrotonPetra_10IN_po_basket_detail-1_large.jpg?v=1630436408', 645000, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
(105, 'Alocasia Polly', 'Alocasia Polly will bring some mid-century style to your home. Also known as the elephant ear, this tropical plant first became popular during the 1950\'s. This seriously striking choice has glossy dark green leaves with thick silver veins, and grows on a thick stem verging on red. Originally from Southeast Asia, they prefer high humidity, bright light, and warm temperatures.', 'alocasia-polly', 46, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/products/Alocacia_Poly_6_DTL1_85d5fcb5-8827-4db9-9de2-90dd59d371ec_large.jpg?v=1611783587', 870000, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
(106, 'Sago Palm', 'One of our favorite patio plants, the Sago Palm, instantly brings a touch of the tropics to your outdoor space. This hardy little beauty is ideal for beginners. They have a tough textured trunk and shiny green leaves. Keep them in a bright spot, and they\'ll thrive. They can also be kept inside and has a reputation as a great air purifier.', 'sago-palm', 97, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/products/pl_sagopalm_6IN_po_grower-detail-1_large.jpg?v=1686250401', 2040000, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
(107, 'Dracaena Lemon Lime', 'Brighten up any space with the lemon-lime dragon tree. They are an indoor plant that thrives in medium light levels, with colorful and spiky leaves that bring drama to any space. With stripes of dark and vivid green and bright yellow, it is easy to see where they get their citrus-inspired name. Adaptable, easy to care for, and air purifying, they are the ideal addition to your desk at work. ...', 'dracaena-lemon-lime', 91, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/products/pl_DracaenaWarneckiiLemonLime_8IN_po_grower_detail-1_large.jpg?v=1628290773', 870000, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
(108, 'Birds Nest Fern', 'Observe the Bird\'s Nest Fern (Asplenium Nidus AGM) fronds as they remind us of a ruffled skirt. This epiphytic tropical, with their lush, leathery leaves, makes a stunning centerpiece. When the new fronds emerge, they resemble bird eggs, hence, their name. At maturity, these will reach 4 feet in length in the right conditions.', 'birds-nest-fern', 66, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/products/Birdsnest_DTL_6_large.jpg?v=1658349099', 870000, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
(109, 'Staghorn Fern', 'Staghorn fern (Platycerium Bifurcatum) makes an attractive ornamental sculpture for a wall indoors or seasonally outdoors in warmer climates. The Royal Horticulture Society Award of Garden Merit gave the nod to this plant in 1993. Their sterile heart-shaped basal fronds overlap and shield the base of the fern\'s roots. Initially dull green and succulent, they turn papery tan to cinnamon-brown ...', 'staghorn-fern', 55, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/products/Staghorn_DTL_4_large.jpg?v=1619466232', 645000, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
(110, 'Calathea Orbifolia', 'Prayer Plant (Calathea orbifolia) can eventually grow to three feet tall but goes at a slow pace. In the meantime, you\'ll have time to count the silvery-green stripes on his slightly large handsome leaves. He plays the camouflage game by folding his leaves upward at night to bare his green leaf underneath like he\'s hiding his stripes to not be as noticeable. His movement gives an exciting ...', 'calathea-orbifolia', 4, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/products/pl_MarantaLemonLime_4IN_po_grower_detail-1_large.jpg?v=1642792437', 870000, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
(111, 'Red Poinsettia: 4 Pack', 'Tis the season to bundle and save!   We can\'t think of a more festive way to introduce the season than this classic and absolutely beautiful holiday plant. The Poinsettia (Euphorbia pulcherrima) is one of the holiday season\'s best picks to make your season cheery and bright.  This bundle includes 4 medium (6\" pot diameter) Red Poinsettia plants.', 'red-poinsettia:-4-pack', 43, 'https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0068/4215/5090/files/Pl_4in_Poinsettia-4-Pack-Bundle_Detail_03_large.jpg?v=1699996288', 1425000, '2024-12-12 18:13:10', '2024-12-12 18:13:10'),
(113, 'Ubi Cilembu', '1 KG 8ribu', 'ubi-cilembu', 10, 'https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/18/Ubi_Cilembu.JPG/1200px-Ubi_Cilembu.JPG', 8000, '2025-01-10 15:55:22', '2025-01-10 15:55:22');

